rows.label: qev093204_MSG0010
rows.name:
Here—the suid meat you were after.
NOW you can give me pizza, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093204_MSG0030
rows.name:
It's actually...kind of impressive.
The lengths you've gone to, just to eat pizza.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093204_MSG0040
rows.name: I told you. When I start something, I see it through.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093204_MSG0050
rows.name:
You never know when life'll deal you a bum hand.
We could shuffle off this coil tomorrow.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093204_MSG0060
rows.name: I don't want any regrets—in anything.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093204_MSG0080
rows.name: You've been real patient with me as well, buddy.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093204_MSG0090
rows.name:
You know, I was just planning for us to
eat out, but... Change of plans.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093204_MSG0100
rows.name:
I'm gonna throw us the pizza party of a lifetime!
Think of it as your reward for all the hard work.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093204_MSG0110
rows.name: Ah, then, you'll be wanting them delivered?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093204_MSG0120
rows.name: Yeah. Send 'em to the BLADE barracks.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093204_MSG0130
rows.name:
And as for the bill...
Commander Vandham at BLADE HQ will foot it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093204_MSG0140
rows.name: Got it! One super-express pizza train comin' right up![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093204_MSG0150
rows.name:
Excellent! And now we wait.
Come on, let's head back.[ST:wait ]
